---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Studio Overview | Palo"
	description="用于测试二级菜单导航的一组实验页入口。"
>
	<main class="page">
		<nav class="crumbs" aria-label="面包屑">
			<a href="/">← Back to Home</a>
		</nav>

		<header class="header">
			<p class="eyebrow">Navigation Sandbox</p>
			<h1>Studio Overview</h1>
			<p class="lead">
				这一组页面专门用来测试二级菜单的展开、激活态、移动端弹出菜单与层级导航表现。
			</p>
		</header>

		<section class="grid">
			<a class="card" href="/studio/navigation-lab">
				<h2>Navigation Lab</h2>
				<p>用于测试当前激活项、返回路径和层级结构。</p>
			</a>
			<a class="card" href="/studio/type-scale-lab">
				<h2>Type Scale Lab</h2>
				<p>用更强层级的标题与正文内容观察排版表现。</p>
			</a>
			<a class="card" href="/studio/glass-panel-lab">
				<h2>Glass Panel Lab</h2>
				<p>用高对比卡片和说明文本观察菜单玻璃背景效果。</p>
			</a>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page {
		max-width: var(--page-max-width);
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2.5rem var(--page-gutter) 5rem;
	}

	.crumbs a {
		display: inline-block;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: var(--text-strong);
		font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
		padding: 0.35rem 0.55rem;
		border-radius: 0.55rem;
	}

	.crumbs a:hover {
		background: rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.06);
		color: var(--link);
	}

	.eyebrow {
		margin: 1rem 0 0.35rem;
		color: var(--muted);
	}

	.header h1 {
		margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
		letter-spacing: -0.03em;
	}

	.lead {
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.card {
		display: block;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: inherit;
		background: var(--card-bg);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 0.95rem;
		padding: 1.25rem;
	}

	.card:hover {
		border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.35);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	.card h2 {
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
	}

	.card p {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.7;
	}
</style>
